'''Google Buzz'''是由[[Google|Google]]开发的[[社交網路服務|社交]]及通訊工具，-{zh:整合;zh-tw:整合;zh-cn:集成}-于该公司的邮件服务[[Gmail|Gmail]]中。<ref name="latimes">{{cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2010/02/google-facebook-social-networking.html|title=Google aims to rival Facebook with new social feature called "Buzz"|last=Guynn|first=Jessica|date=2010-02-09|publisher=LA Times|accessdate=9 February 2010|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305015321/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2010/02/google-facebook-social-networking.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gearlive.com/news/article/q110-google-buzz-announced/|title=Google Buzz announced|last=Edwards|first=Andru|date=2010-02-09|publisher=Gearlive|accessdate=9 February 2010|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017140827/http://www.gearlive.com/news/article/q110-google-buzz-announced/|dead-url=no}}</ref>朋友分享的-{A|zh:連結;zh-tw:連結;zh-cn:链接}-与信息会显示在Gmail界面中。<ref name="gizmodo-launch">{{cite web|url=http://gizmodo.com/5467843/live-from-googles-february-event-google-goes-social|title=Live From Google's February Event: Google Gets Twittery|last=Herrman|first=John|date=2010-02-09|publisher=Gizmodo|accessdate=9 February 2010|archive-date=2012-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121008110630/http://gizmodo.com/5467843/live-from-googles-february-event-google-goes-social|dead-url=no}}</ref>Buzz中融合了照片、视频、链接等多种元素，形成了Gmail会话的重要组成部分。

用户在发布Buzz时可以选择将其分享给全世界或是有限人群。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gmailblog.blogspot.com/2010/02/google-buzz-in-gmail.html |title=Blog announcement |accessdate=2010-02-11 |archive-date=2015-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119034255/http://gmailblog.blogspot.com/2010/02/google-buzz-in-gmail.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>Buzz支援[[Picasa|Picasa]]、[[Flickr|Flickr]]、[[Google_Reader|Google Reader]]、[[YouTube|YouTube]]、[[Blogger|Blogger]]和[[Twitter|Twitter]]。Buzz的建立被认为是Google对如[[Facebook|Facebook]]之类的[[社交網路服務|社交網路服務]]的一种尝试<ref name="latimes" />。Buzz也借用了[[FriendFeed|FriendFeed]]等网站的界面元素，例如对一则消息可以表示“喜好”。

Google的[[谢尔盖·布林|谢尔盖·布林]]表示，借助Buzz，人们可以在工作和休闲之间建立桥梁，拉近距离。<ref name="nytimes">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/10/technology/internet/10social.html|title=With Buzz, Google Plunges Into Social Networking|last=Helft|first=Miguel|date=2010-02-09|publisher=NY Times|accessdate=11 February 2010|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112182101/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/10/technology/internet/10social.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[Google+|Google+]]全面開放之後，Google公司於2011年底停止Google Buzz服務<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mag.udn.com/mag/digital/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=348420|title=Google Buzz服務喊卡 押寶社群網|publisher=經濟日報|date=2011-10-16|accessdate=2011-10-17|archive-date=2011-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111219013447/http://mag.udn.com/mag/digital/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=348420|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 移动版 ==
通过移动设备（如iPod Touch）使用Buzz，用户的当前位置会被标识出来。用户可以在隐私设置里调整位置显示的精确度——显示精确的地点，或只是所在城市等等。用户只允许使用内置的[[GPS|GPS]]定位，而不可以使用通过[[Google_Latitude|Google Latitude]]自定义的地标。

移动版同时结合了[[Google_Maps|Google Maps]]，所以用户可以知道有哪些其他用户在周围。通过Google Maps发布的Buzz消息是公开的，任何使用软件的人都可看见。移动版用户可以发送文字和照片。目前移动版只支持[[Android|Android]] 2.0+、iPhone/iPod Touch、[[Windows_Mobile|Windows Mobile]]以及[[S60|S60]]。<ref name="gizmodo-launch" />

== 历史 ==
2010年2月9日Google在[[芒廷维尤_(加利福尼亚州)|山景城]]总部宣布了这项计划，并于当天[[太平洋时间|太平洋时间]]11时发布。<ref>{{cite web | title=Google Goes Social with Google Buzz | url=http://mashable.com/2010/02/09/google-buzz/ | publisher=[[Mashable|Mashable]] | accessdate=10 February 2010 | archive-date=2015-09-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905155705/http://mashable.com/2010/02/09/google-buzz/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>在接下来的数周内，Google Buzz功能将逐渐开放给所有Gmail账户，并集合在Gmail界面中。同时在Android和iPhone平台的版本也发布了。<ref name="gizmodo-launch" />

== 反响 ==

=== 隐私 ===
部分Google Buzz的功能引发了与Facebook类似的关于隐私的担忧。<ref>{{cite news |title=Google Buzz Privacy Concerns Similiar to Facebook Issues |author=Brian Prince |date=2010-02-10 |work=[[eWeek|eWeek]] |url=http://www.eweek.com/c/a/Security/Google-Buzz-Privacy-Concerns-Similiar-to-Facebook-Issues-629697/}}</ref>然而，最为诟病的一项设置是，Buzz会默认公开与一个Gmail账户交流最紧密的联系人。<ref>{{cite news |title=Google Buzz Criticized for Disclosing Gmail Contacts |author=Robert McMillan |date=2010-02-10 |publisher=[[IDG_News_Service|IDG News Service]] |url=http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/189081/google_buzz_criticized_for_disclosing_gmail_contacts.html |accessdate=2010-02-11 |archive-date=2011-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111216070219/http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/189081/google_buzz_criticized_for_disclosing_gmail_contacts.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=WARNING: Google Buzz Has A Huge Privacy Flaw |author=Nicholas Carlson |date=2010-02-10 |work=[[The_Business_Insider|The Business Insider]] |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/warning-google-buzz-has-a-huge-privacy-flaw-2010-2 |accessdate=2010-02-11 |archive-date=2010-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100212070754/http://www.businessinsider.com/warning-google-buzz-has-a-huge-privacy-flaw-2010-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

